SingleColumn.Caption:
from decisionhistory select current
(
if(decisiontype = 'Query') then translate("#LDS#Query")
else if(decisiontype = 'Answer') then translate("#LDS#Answer")
else datacaption(decisionhistory,reasonhead)
)

Function.Expression:
